divs: sighting detailsi was facing north on 3700 cottage grove avenue in des moines ia. the object appeared eastward bright in the sky. the object moved slowly but in a straight path. the object resembled an orb emitting a white\red glow. the object was at the same level of the stratus clouds and moved in-sequence with the pace of the stratus cloud. the orb's light faded until it dissolved.
